text: Rui Soares (born 5 October 1993 in Porto) is a Portuguese professional squash player.https://psaworldtour.com/players/view/3645/rui-soares As of March 2018, he was ranked number 113 in the world, and number 1 in Portugal. He has competed in the main draw of multiple professional PSA tournaments. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male squash players
